p class=3D"text-[14px] leading-[150%] break-words whitespace-break-spaces w=
rap-anywhere">You are an expert Full Stack Software Engineer and UI/UX Desi=
gner.

I want you to build a complete Personal Competitive Programming IDE.

This project is ONLY for personal use.

Do NOT build authentication, user accounts, login, signup, profile pages, a=
dmin panels, email verification, OAuth, cloud sync, or any multi-user funct=
ionality.

The application should launch directly into the IDE.

=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=
=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=
=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=
=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=
=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81

PROJECT NAME

Forge IDE

=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=
=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=
=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=
=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=
=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81

PROJECT GOAL

Create a modern competitive programming IDE that combines:

=E2=80=A2 LeetCode's beautiful UI/UX
=E2=80=A2 VS Code's editing experience
=E2=80=A2 CodeChef's simplicity

This is NOT an online judge.

This is a local coding environment capable of compiling and executing multi=
ple programming languages.

Everything should feel extremely polished.

=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=
=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=
=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=
=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=
=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81

DESIGN STYLE

The entire application should look inspired by LeetCode.

Dark Theme.

Minimal.

Professional.

No unnecessary animations.

Smooth.

Fast.

Modern.

Rounded corners.

Subtle shadows.

Beautiful typography.

Use lots of spacing.

No cyberpunk theme.

No glowing neon.

No gradients everywhere.

Very clean.

=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=
=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=
=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=
=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=
=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81

