=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=
=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81

TYPOGRAPHY

UI Font

Inter

Editor Font

JetBrains Mono

=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=
=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=
=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=
=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=
=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81=E2=94=81

LAYOUT

There should ONLY be THREE WORKSPACES.

Nothing else.

NO sidebar.

NO problem statement.

NO dashboard.

NO statistics.

NO profile.

NO recent activity.

NO left navigation.

Only

1. Code Editor

2. Input

3. Output

Layout

---------------------------------------------------------
|                                                       |
|                 Monaco Code Editor                    |
|                                                       |
|                                                       |
|                                                       |
|                                                       |
---------------------------------------------------------
|            Input            |         Output          |
|                             |                         |
|                             |                         |
|                             |                         |
---------------------------------------------------------

The editor occupies approximately 70% of the height.

Bottom section occupies approximately 30%.

Bottom should be split equally:

Left:
Input

Right:
Output

